          "_name": "content4",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section content4\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Góra\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Dół\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Pokaż tytuł\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Pokaż podtytuł\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Pokaż przyciski\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Kolor ta\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-8\">\n                <h2 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><div>How to play and win at UNO?\n</div></h2>\n                <h3 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>You must first shuffle the cards. Then put the first number card on the table. It is she who will start our game. Each player receives 7 cards, which he arranges like a fan. The gameplay consists in matching one of his cards in terms of color, shape or symbol to the face up. If we do not have one, we are left to draw another card.\n</div><div>\n</div><div>There are also special cards here. For example, when we draw Take two, it means that the next player must take two cards. When a stop is involved, the next player loses his turn. There are several types of these types of cards that make the game much more dynamic and unpredictable, because we never know what our predecessor will draw and what will treat us.\n</div><div>\n</div><div>And where did the name of the game come from? When a player realizes that he has only one card in his hand, he must shout UNO quickly! (i.e. one). The winner is the person who gets rid of the cards. What do all players strive for? Their goal is to get 500 points, taking into account the basic version of the game. It's good to know that there are many more versions, there are various variations and changes thanks to which this game based on the executioner deck never gets bored.\n</div><div>\n</div><div>You can take it with you anywhere, it won't take a lot of space in your backpack or suitcase. We will spread out the cards wherever we feel like it.\n</div><div>\n</div><div>Mattel has prepared a lot of propositions for this title for fans of card games, besides the classic one, for example, the cards have been additionally enriched with fabulously colorful characters. Certainly, such a UNO option will appeal to all kids!<br>Read more about drunk Uno here: <a href=\"https://www.ringoffirerules.com/drunk-uno-game-rules/\">https://www.ringoffirerules.com/drunk-uno-game-rules/</a></div></h3>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center py-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">DOWIEDZ SIĘ WIĘCEJ</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">DEMO</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
